---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Services - Web Design, Development, SEO & PPC | DC technolabs"
  description="Comprehensive digital services in Ahmedabad: Professional web design, custom development, SEO optimization, and PPC management. Get a free consultation today."
>
  <Header />
  
  <div style="height: 80px;"></div>
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Comprehensive digital solutions to grow your business online</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Services Detail -->
  <section class="section services-detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="service-header">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>Web Design</h2>
              <p class="service-tagline">Beautiful, user-friendly designs that convert</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p>Your website is often the first impression potential customers have of your business. We create stunning, modern websites that not only look great but are designed to convert visitors into customers.</p>
          
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Custom responsive design for all devices</li>
            <li>User experience (UX) optimization</li>
            <li>Brand-aligned visual identity</li>
            <li>Interactive elements and animations</li>
            <li>Mobile-first approach</li>
            <li>Fast loading times</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="service-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            <a href="/services/web-design" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-block reverse">
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="service-header">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>Web Development</h2>
              <p class="service-tagline">Powerful, scalable web applications</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p>From simple brochure websites to complex web applications, we build robust, secure, and scalable solutions using the latest technologies. Your website will be fast, reliable, and built to grow with your business.</p>
          
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Custom web application development</li>
            <li>E-commerce solutions (Shopify, WooCommerce)</li>
            <li>WordPress CMS development</li>
            <li>API integration and development</li>
            <li>Database design and optimization</li>
            <li>Ongoing maintenance and support</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="service-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            <a href="/services/web-development" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="service-header">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
                <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>SEO Services</h2>
              <p class="service-tagline">Rank higher, get more organic traffic</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p>Get found by customers searching for your services in Ahmedabad and across Gujarat. Our proven SEO strategies help you rank higher on Google, drive qualified traffic, and increase conversions.</p>
          
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Comprehensive SEO audit</li>
            <li>Keyword research and strategy</li>
            <li>On-page optimization</li>
            <li>Local SEO for Ahmedabad</li>
            <li>Content optimization</li>
            <li>Link building and authority growth</li>
            <li>Monthly reporting and analytics</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="service-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            <a href="/services/seo" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-block reverse">
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="service-header">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
                <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>PPC Management</h2>
              <p class="service-tagline">Maximize ROI with expert ad campaigns</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p>Get immediate results with targeted Google Ads and Facebook advertising campaigns. We create, manage, and optimize your PPC campaigns to deliver maximum return on investment.</p>
          
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Google Ads campaign setup and management</li>
            <li>Facebook and Instagram advertising</li>
            <li>Landing page optimization</li>
            <li>A/B testing and conversion optimization</li>
            <li>Keyword research and bidding strategy</li>
            <li>Detailed performance reporting</li>
            <li>Budget optimization</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="service-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            <a href="/services/ppc" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Digital Presence?</h2>
        <p>Get a free consultation and custom proposal for your business</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent btn-large">Get Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--secondary-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }
  
  .page-hero h1 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .services-detail {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }
  
  .service-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .service-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .service-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .service-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .service-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-tagline {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .service-content > p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .service-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .feature-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
  
  .feature-list li::before {
    content: 'âœ“';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .service-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-content h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .service-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .service-cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
